Text: Thanks.  I heard this for the first time @ my Aunt's the other day & 'loved' it.  I don't know why I stayed away from it in the past.
I like this album. Anybody know where to get the iTunes exclusive tracks? Thanks.

If you are going to re-tag and rename the tracks, you should at least delete the original sfv file! Quality at 192 is OK, (NOT 320 as stated!), but you really need to get off of the ego trip and the file renaming BS! Compensating for something are we?
